{"id":"15ae45db-d828-4348-9589-2759a66d8180","name":"Alpha Gardevoir","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">An Alpha Gardevoir resides in the Alabaster Icelands, proceed with caution. Alpha Pokémon are known to be extremely territorial and dangerous... Though this one in specific seems to be slightly curious. Still, be careful as to not intrude.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 230, 106)\"><strong><em>Pokémon Legends: Arceus</em></strong></span><strong>.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 245, 163)\">[Art is by @tomiyu25, go show them support if you like the art! Their work is incredible!]</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 172, 172)\"><em>(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/11bc29e3-bf27-4c43-b64e-9e6ee55c124e_character-meowscarada-your-starter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Meowscarada</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- Your trusty starter in the Paldea region from Pokémon Scarlet/Violet.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5f4fc08f-528b-4177-b91f-172e853f62db_character-zinnia-draconid-lorekeeper\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Zinnia</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- Lorekeeper of the Draconids from Pokémon Omega Ruby/Alpha Sapphire.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: cen